data.description: Welcome to this stunning brick three-bedroom, two-bathroom move in ready ranch nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac. This home is practically brand new with fresh paint, appliances, cabinets, fixtures and HVAC and a huge crawl space for storage ! Boasting a prime location and a beautifully updated interior, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. Step inside to discover a bright and airy floor plan, enhanced by modern finishes and thoughtful design details throughout. The spacious living room is perfect for lounging and entertainment. The kitchen is a chef's dream with custom cabinetry, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. When preparing a meal, this kitchen has everything you need to create culinary delights. Each of the three bedrooms has been tastefully redone & renovated, the luxurious bathrooms are equally impressive, featuring stylish vanities and contemporary fixtures, Outside, you'll find a private backyard oasis, perfect for outdoor living and entertaining, with lush landscaping, this serene setting is ideal. Located in a sought-after cul-de-sac neighborhood, this exceptional home combines convenience with tranquility, offering easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Home includes refrigerator, stove, microwave, dishwasher, washer, dryer and crawl space dehumidifier with the sale. Don't miss this opportunity to own a beautifully renovated ranch in a prime location. Schedule your private showing today!
